ResistanceGA2 1.1.14
---------
* Optimized gdistance commute runs with batched sparse solves and selected-pair gdistance runs by reusing endpoint distance calculations
* Added a vectorized sparse transition builder for the default gdistance transition function on projected 4- and 8-neighbor rasters
* Added a vectorized projected-raster geographic correction path for gdistance transition matrices
* Tuned the sparse Cholesky strategy used by fast gdistance commute-distance solves on large rasters
* Reduced peak memory and solve time for exact gdistance commute-distance runs by solving endpoint right-hand sides in blocks
* Cached projected-raster gdistance transition geometry across repeated calls with identical raster geometry and directions
* Added an opt-in aggregate approximation for iterative gdistance commute-distance optimization runs
* Added benchmark scripts comparing optimized gdistance commute runs with Julia/Circuitscape and aggregate approximations

ResistanceGA2 1.1.13
---------
* Made the Julia_Guide connection-verification chunks display-only so vignette rebuilds do not depend on starting Julia during package checks

ResistanceGA2 1.1.12
---------
* Made the Julia_Guide vignette detect Julia automatically so vignette rebuilds do not fail on systems without a local Julia installation
* Restored normal vignette builds in the GitHub Actions package-check workflow

ResistanceGA2 1.1.11
---------
* Excluded GitHub workflow files from built package contents and aligned CI package checks with the standard no-vignette pre-check workflow

ResistanceGA2 1.1.10
